nding on density, preferences, available forms and purposes."}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Bulk","prefLabel":{"en":"Bulk","de":"Schüttgut","fr":"Vrac"},"definition":{"en":"Loose building materials used to fill voids"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Massive","prefLabel":{"en":"Massive","de":"Massivbau","fr":"Massif"},"definition":{"en":"Building Materials that can be processed to become massive, homogene building elements. They can be load-bearing or not and are mostly in need of formwork. "}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Mortar","prefLabel":{"en":"Mortar, Plaster","de":"Mörtel, Putz","fr":"Mortier, Crépis"},"definition":{"en":"Mixes of a binder, fillers and sometimes additives to bond brick or to plaster or render surfaces."}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Panel","prefLabel":{"en":"Panel","de":"Platten","fr":"Plaques"},"definition":{"en":"Prefabricated flat building materials, designed for different purposes as panelling and/or insulation"}}]},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/NaturalResource","prefLabel":{"en":"Resource","de":"Ressourcen","fr":"Ressources"},"definition":{"en":"Resources that can potentially be used for construction; both occuring naturally (like bio- or geo-sourced) or being salvaged from demoltions."},"narrower":[{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Earth","prefLabel":{"en":"Earth","de":"Lehm","fr":"Terre"},"definition":{"en":"Naturally occuring resource in the sub-soil containing clay as binder for silts and sands in different proportions."}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Hemp","prefLabel":{"en":"Hemp","de":"Hanf","fr":"Chanvre"},"definition":{"en":"Hemp"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/OtherFiber","prefLabel":{"en":"Other Fibre","de":"Andere Fasern","fr":"Autres fibres"},"definition":{"en":"Fibrous plants other than cereals or hemp"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Rock","prefLabel":{"en":"Rock","de":"Gestein","fr":"Roche"},"definition":{"en":"Natural rocks that can be found the bedrock"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Straw","prefLabel":{"en":"Straw","de":"Stroh","fr":"Paille"},"definition":{"en":"Dried stalks of cereals"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Wood","prefLabel":{"en":"Wood","de":"Holz","fr":"Bois"},"definition":{"en":"Wood"}}]},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Construction","prefLabel":{"en":"Construction","de":"Bauwerk","fr":"Construction"},"definition":{"en":"Constructions using building materials to become building elements."},"narrower":[{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Structure","prefLabel":{"en":"Structure","de":"Struktur","fr":"Structure"},"definition":{"en":"Load-bearing elements of a building"},"narrower":[{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Balcony","prefLabel":{"en":"Balcony","de":"Balkon"},"definition":{"en":"Structure outside exterior wall"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Ceiling","prefLabel":{"en":"Ceiling","de":"Decke"},"definition":{"en":"Separation between storeys"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Column","prefLabel":{"en":"Column","de":"Stütze"},"definition":{"en":"Load-bearing elements, usually indoors"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/ExteriorWallAboveGround","prefLabel":{"en":"Exterior Wall Above Ground","de":"Aussenwand Über Terrain"},"definition":{"en":"Wall that separates the exterior from the interior of the building above ground"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/ExteriorWallUnderGround","prefLabel":{"en":"Exterior Wall Under Ground","de":"Aussenwand Unter Terrain"},"definition":{"en":"Wall that separates the exterior from the interior of the building under ground"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/FloorSlabGroundFloor","prefLabel":{"en":"Floor Slab Ground Floor","de":"Bodenplatte EG","fr":"Dalle Rez-de-chaussée"},"definition":{"en":"Slab that represents the floor at ground level"}},{"id":"https://ontology.atlas-regenmat.ch/Foundation","prefLabel":{"en":"Foundation","de"